{"at":"2026-06-06T00:37:22Z","commit_ref":"ade1bd7","decision":"include","gate":"build","rationale":"Spec 0026 adds many net-new .fs files across OpticalConstructor.Domain/.Storage/.Ui/.App and new test projects (Files in scope) and extends project files; the universal build gate (dotnet build Berreman.slnx) covers compilation of every file in scope. applies_to Berreman/**/*.fs|*.fsproj|*.slnx matches."}
{"at":"2026-06-06T00:37:22Z","commit_ref":"ade1bd7","decision":"include","gate":"unit-tests","rationale":"Spec reuses the pure solver as-is (constraint 0.1: BeamTree.fs:91, Units.fs) and the gate's broad applies_to (Berreman/**/*.fs) matches the new Domain files; run BerremanTests as a regression guard that the reused engine still passes. Default-inclusion bias."}
{"at":"2026-06-06T00:37:22Z","commit_ref":"ade1bd7","decision":"include","gate":"constructor-unit-tests","rationale":"Covers the UI-less Domain/Storage test surface in Files in scope: PlacementTests.fs (Part A), RayModelTests.fs (Part B), GroupsRoundTripTests.fs + project round-trip fixture (A.8/C.1/G/H) under OpticalConstructor.Tests. applies_to Berreman/OpticalConstructor/** matches."}
{"at":"2026-06-06T00:37:22Z","commit_ref":"ade1bd7","decision":"include","gate":"ui-smoke","rationale":"Spec adds a net-new constructor page, ribbon shell, drawer and App/Program.fs startup wiring (Parts C/D/E/I); the headless launch/render smoke gate over OpticalConstructor.Ui/.App guards that every view renders a frame without throwing (UX commitment 4)."}
{"at":"2026-06-06T00:37:22Z","commit_ref":"ade1bd7","decision":"include","gate":"ui-tests","rationale":"Covers the per-panel view tests added under OpticalConstructor.Ui.Tests: CommandRegistryTests.fs (Part E / AC-E1), LocalizationTests.fs (Part I), ConstructorViewTests.fs (Parts C/J). applies_to OpticalConstructor.Ui.Tests/** matches."}
{"at":"2026-06-06T00:37:22Z","commit_ref":"ade1bd7","decision":"include","gate":"impl-log-structure","rationale":"Universal root-level structural check on the slice impl-log MD; per .gates/.gates-md it applies to every slice and excluding it would break the spec-writer workflow itself."}
